:R-HSA-428559  a            obo:GO_0008150 , owl:NamedIndividual ;
        rdfs:comment        "The human SLC36A gene family encodes four proton-coupled neutral amino acid transporters, PAT1-4. PAT1 and 2 mediate electroneutral symport of protons and small neutral amino acids like glycine, alanine and proline. PAT3 and 4 are orphans with unknown function (Boll M et al, 2004)." ;
        rdfs:label          "Proton-coupled neutral amino acid transporters" ;
        dc:contributor      "Authored: Jassal, Bijay, 2009-07-06" , "Edited: Jassal, Bijay, 2009-07-06" , "GOC:reactome_curators" , "Reviewed: He, L, 2009-08-24" ;
